k paste recipe.","To make your own mayonnaise, refer to the recipe in <i>The Basic Cookbook<\/i> or <i>Everyday Cookbook<\/i>.","We serve this dish right in the ramekin, but to turn it out, simply line your ramekins with plastic wrap - allowing approx. 5 cm of overhang - before filling with pâté. Once chilled, use the plastic wrap to easily remove it from the ramekins.","<strong>Crayfish pâté<\/strong>: Replace the hot smoked trout with 200 g cooked crayfish, then proceed as per recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","3h 15m","4 portions"]}